        How does it work?
        Browse activities online today. Attend activities in real life tomorrow!
        </blockquote>
        
        <h4>What would you like to do first? </h4>
        <%= link_to "Browse activities", activities_path, class: "btn btn-large btn-primary" %>
        <%= link_to "Edit your user profile", edit_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-large btn-primary" %>
        <hr>
        <ul>
            <li><b>Sign up</b> to see activities near your location</li>
            <li><b>Browse</b> the descriptions of dozens of activities</li>
